rows.label: qst105909_msg001
rows.name:
Oh, you're back. Did you manage
to sell the small Ether Reactor?

rows.label: qst105909_msg002
rows.name:
It was bought for 12,000G?! I knew
it was valuable, but I never thought
it would sell for that much...

rows.label: qst105909_msg003
rows.name:
It seems leaving it to you
was the right choice. You
really helped me out.

rows.label: qst105909_msg004
rows.name:
You've come this far with me, so I
have to give you a proper reward.

rows.label: qst105909_msg005
rows.name:
It may not be enough for all your
work, but please accept it.

rows.label: qst105909_msg006
rows.name:
I'll try to do my best with the
funds you've earned for me.

rows.label: qst105909_msg007
rows.name:
Well then, I'll be going now. I have
to get my preparations underway.

rows.label: qst105909_msg008
rows.name:
I'd be happy if you stopped
by when the shop opens.
